456 public void Populate(BestiaryDatabase database)
457 {
458 _currentDatabase = database;
459 AddEmptyEntries_CrittersAndEnemies_Automated();
460 AddTownNPCs_Manual();
461 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_Automated();
462 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_Manual();
463 AddNPCBiomeRelationships_AddDecorations_Automated();
464 ModifyEntriesThatNeedIt();
465 RegisterFilters();
466 RegisterSortSteps();
467 }
468
469 private void RegisterTestEntries()
470 {
471 Register(BestiaryEntry.Biome("Bestiary_Biomes.Hallow", "Images/UI/Bestiary/Biome_Hallow", Conditions.ReachHardMode));
472 }
473
474 private void RegisterSortSteps()
475 {
476 foreach (IBestiarySortStep item in new List<IBestiarySortStep>
477 {
478 new SortingSteps.ByUnlockState(),
479 new SortingSteps.ByBestiarySortingId(),
480 new SortingSteps.Alphabetical(),
481 new SortingSteps.ByNetId(),
482 new SortingSteps.ByAttack(),
483 new SortingSteps.ByDefense(),
484 new SortingSteps.ByCoins(),
485 new SortingSteps.ByHP(),
486 new SortingSteps.ByBestiaryRarity()
487 })
488 {
489 _currentDatabase.Register(item);
490 }
491 }
492
493 private void RegisterFilters()
494 {
495 Register(new Filters.ByUnlockState());
496 Register(new Filters.ByBoss());
497 Register(new Filters.ByRareCreature());
498 List<IBestiaryInfoElement> commonInfoElementsForFilters = CommonTags.GetCommonInfoElementsForFilters();
499 for (int i = 0; i < commonInfoElementsForFilters.Count; i++)
500 {
501 Register(new Filters.ByInfoElement(commonInfoElementsForFilters[i]));
502 }
503 }
504
505 private void ModifyEntriesThatNeedIt_NameOverride(int npcID, string newNameKey)
506 {
507 BestiaryEntry bestiaryEntry = FindEntryByNPCID(npcID);
508 bestiaryEntry.Info.RemoveAll((IBestiaryInfoElement x) => x is NamePlateInfoElement);
509 bestiaryEntry.Info.Add(new NamePlateInfoElement(newNameKey, npcID));
510 bestiaryEntry.Icon = new UnlockableNPCEntryIcon(npcID, 0f, 0f, 0f, 0f, newNameKey);
511 }

674 private void TryGivingEntryFlavorTextIfItIsMissing(BestiaryEntry entry)
675 {
676 if (entry.Info.Any((IBestiaryInfoElement x) => x is FlavorTextBestiaryInfoElement))
677 {
678 return;
679 }
680 SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = null;
681 int? num = null;
682 foreach (IBestiaryInfoElement item in entry.Info)
683 {
684 if (item is BestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement bestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement && bestiaryPortraitBackgroundProviderPreferenceInfoElement.GetPreferredProvider() is SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement2)
685 {
686 spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement2;
687 break;
688 }
689 if (item is SpawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement { DisplayTextPriority: var displayTextPriority } spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement3 && (!num.HasValue || displayTextPriority >= num))
690 {
691 spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement3;
692 num = displayTextPriority;
693 }
694 }
695 if (spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement != null)
696 {
697 string displayNameKey = spawnConditionBestiaryInfoElement.GetDisplayNameKey();
698 string text = "Bestiary_BiomeText.biome_";
699 string text2 = displayNameKey.Substring(displayNameKey.IndexOf('.') + 1);
700 text += text2;
701 entry.Info.Add(new FlavorTextBestiaryInfoElement(text));
702 }
703 }

754 private void AddEmptyEntries_CrittersAndEnemies_Automated()
755 {
756 HashSet<int> exclusions = GetExclusions();
757 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPC> item in ContentSamples.NpcsByNetId)
758 {
759 if (!exclusions.Contains(item.Key) && !item.Value.isLikeATownNPC)
760 {
761 if (item.Value.CountsAsACritter)
762 {
763 Register(BestiaryEntry.Critter(item.Key));
764 }
765 else
766 {
767 Register(BestiaryEntry.Enemy(item.Key));
768 }
769 }
770 }
771 }
772
773 private static HashSet<int> GetExclusions()
774 {
775 HashSet<int> hashSet = new HashSet<int>();
776 List<int> list = new List<int>();
777 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPCID.Sets.NPCBestiaryDrawModifiers> item in NPCID.Sets.NPCBestiaryDrawOffset)
778 {
779 if (item.Value.Hide)
780 {
781 list.Add(item.Key);
782 }
783 }
784 foreach (int item2 in list)
785 {
786 hashSet.Add(item2);
787 }
788 return hashSet;
789 }

1924 private void AddNPCBiomeRelationships_AddDecorations_Automated()
1925 {
1926 foreach (KeyValuePair<int, NPC> item in ContentSamples.NpcsByNetId)
1927 {
1928 BestiaryEntry bestiaryEntry = FindEntryByNPCID(item.Key);
1929 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Events.Rain))
1930 {
1931 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Biomes.Snow))
1932 {
1933 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Blizzard);
1934 }
1935 else
1936 {
1937 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Rain);
1938 }
1939 continue;
1940 }
1941 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Events.Eclipse))
1942 {
1943 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.EclipseSun);
1944 }
1945 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Times.NightTime))
1946 {
1947 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Moon);
1948 }
1949 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Times.DayTime))
1950 {
1951 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Sun);
1952 }
1953 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Invasions.PumpkinMoon))
1954 {
1955 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.PumpkinMoon);
1956 }
1957 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Invasions.FrostMoon))
1958 {
1959 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.FrostMoon);
1960 }
1961 if (bestiaryEntry.Info.Contains(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Biomes.Meteor))
1962 {
1963 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Moon);
1964 bestiaryEntry.AddTags(CommonTags.SpawnConditions.Visuals.Meteor);
1965 }
1966 }
1967 }
